            <thetext>A corresponding bug has been opened in the RAP bugzilla:
Bug 279800: Some focused widgets look strange in webkit (https://bugs.eclipse.org/bugs/show_bug.cgi?id=279800)

This could be also seen easily in Qooxdoo 0.7.4 Demo Borwser:
1. Open the demo browser
2. Open example &quot;Button 1&quot; under Samples/example
(http://demo.qooxdoo.org/0.7.4/demobrowser/#example~Button_1.html)
3. Focus one of the enabled buttons with mouse click or TAB
4. See the additional thick glowing frame around the button, together with the typical dotted focus frame.</thetext>
